name: Corneo's D.va (Overwatch) Embedding
description:
This is a textual inversion embedding for D.va (Hana Song) from Overwatch.

Use corneo_dva to activate. It's a little overfit so you might want to de-emphasise it in some situations to (corneo_dva:0.9) or (corneo_dva:0.95). It also works best below about 11 CFG value.

Example images produced with OrangeCocoa available here https://civitai.com/models/4355/orangecocoa-5050-mix

Check out my other civitai models for more characters and sex positions! https://civitai.com/user/Master_Corneo

If you enjoy this embed, I genuinely love seeing your creations with it - you can attach them to a review if you're not aware (but not comments sadly)!

modelVersions.description:
BIG UPDATE! Turns out an extension I was using as part of my embedding creation just, er, doesn't work most of the time, so all of my training data and embeddings so far have been a bit wrong.

Put this theory to the test by re-training D.va here and it's right, the embedding is much more accurate now, especially things like the eyes didn't really work correctly before and you had to tag brown_eyes and they still looked bad. Now you should get somewhat decent eyes by default!
